{"id":2,"date":"2026-01-20","title":"Données initiales - AIMS, AMADEUS, RAPID","description":"Import initial des données du 20 janvier 2026.\\nPremière réception de données des systèmes principaux :\\n- AIMS : Programme de vol (FLT)\\n- AMADEUS : Datafeeds passagers (APS, DCS, HOTE/LIFT, PNR, TDNA, Inventaire)\\n- RAPID/ACCELYA : Revenue Accounting (FLP, IBP, SLP)\\n\\nCes données ont permis de documenter les premiers flux entre les systèmes PSS et Revenue Accounting.","import_type":"DATAFEED","status":"SUCCESS","source_folder":"data/20_01","systems_added":0,"flows_added":0,"formats_added":5,"fields_added":12,"samples_added":3,"details_json":{"flows": [], "fields": [{"name": "Record Type", "type": "Num", "format": "SSIM", "description": "Type d enregistrement"}, {"name": "Airline Code", "type": "Alpha", "format": "SSIM", "description": "Code IATA compagnie"}, {"name": "Flight Number", "type": "Alphanum", "format": "SSIM", "description": "Numéro de vol"}, {"name": "Service Type", "type": "Alpha", "format": "SSIM", "description": "Type de service"}, {"name": "Period From", "type": "Date", "format": "SSIM", "description": "Début période"}, {"name": "Period To", "type": "Date", "format": "SSIM", "description": "Fin période"}], "formats": [{"code": "SSIM", "name": "Standard Schedules Information Manual", "standard": "IATA", "description": "Format standard IATA pour le programme de vol"}, {"code": "SSM", "name": "Standard Schedule Message", "standard": "IATA", "description": "Message de modification du programme de vol"}, {"code": "ASM", "name": "Ad hoc Schedule Message", "standard": "IATA", "description": "Message de modification ponctuelle"}, {"code": "MVT", "name": "Movement Message", "standard": "IATA", "description": "Message de mouvement avion"}, {"code": "LDM", "name": "Load Message", "standard": "IATA", "description": "Message de chargement avion"}], "samples": [{"name": "AIMS FLT", "type": "FLT", "source": "AIMS", "description": "Programme de vol journalier"}, {"